name: MickiMy-TheVowelSong
0:
”Alexa, open Micki My for the letter D”
”Do Micki My for the letter D”
”Do Micki My D”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: micki my
des:
Micki My teaches you a little ditty made famous by the Three Stooges, with help from Professor Moe and others along the way. Make a request using only a consonant from the alphabet (vs a vowel) lest you be scolded.

Open Micki My by saying things like "Open Micki My" or "Load Micki My". Make a request by saying things like "Do Micki My for the letter D" or "Do Micki My D". You can both open the app and make a request in one-shot by saying things like "Open Micki My for the letter D".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
